+## backup github
+
+Creates a redacted backup package in the local knowledge-bank repository.
+
+By default, this command writes files locally and does not commit or push.
+
+```text
+python pala.py backup github
+```
+
+Use a custom knowledge-bank path:
+
+```text
+python pala.py backup github --knowledge-bank C:\path\to\pala-os-bilgi-bankasi
+```
+
+Commit the package:
+
+```text
+python pala.py backup github --commit
+```
+
+Commit and push the package:
+
+```text
+python pala.py backup github --push
+```
+
+Default path:
+
+```text
+%USERPROFILE%\Desktop\Codex\pala-os-bilgi-bankasi
+```
+
 ## dashboard export
 
 Writes today's local records to `dashboard/records.json` so the static dashboard can show real captured data.
