+## GitHub Backup Defaults
+
+`pala backup github` creates a redacted package and does not commit or push unless explicitly requested.
+
+| Mode | Behavior |
+|---|---|
+| default | Write package locally |
+| `--commit` | Commit package in the knowledge-bank repo |
+| `--push` | Commit and push package |
+
+Raw conversation text is not copied by default. Full-fidelity backups should use private storage.
