+# v0.4 GitHub Backup
+
+Date: 2026-06-09
+Phase: knowledge-bank backup connector preview
+Status: PASS for redacted knowledge-bank backup package
+
+## Goal
+
+Create a safe first GitHub backup path by writing a redacted backup package into a local `pala-os-bilgi-bankasi` checkout.
+
+## Added Behavior
+
+| Area | Change |
+|---|---|
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py backup github` |
+| Default target | `%USERPROFILE%\Desktop\Codex\pala-os-bilgi-bankasi` |
+| Output folder | `reports/pala-memory-core-backups/<date-stamp>/` |
+| Default mode | Write local package only |
+| Optional mode | `--commit` or `--push` |
+| Safety | Common API key/token/private key patterns are redacted |
+
+## Commands
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py backup github
+python .\pala.py backup github --commit
+python .\pala.py backup github --push
+```
+
+## Expected Package
+
+| File | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `backup-report.md` | Human-readable summary |
+| `records-manifest.json` | Redacted record manifest |
+| `backup-receipt.json` | Backup receipt |
+| `artifacts/` | Redacted brief/receipt/dashboard exports when present |
+
+## Smoke Test
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py backup github --push
+```
+
+Observed output:
+
+```text
+github backup package saved C:\Users\Pala-Home-1\Desktop\Codex\pala-os-bilgi-bankasi\reports\pala-memory-core-backups\2026-06-09-20260609T131949Z-pala-memory-core-backup
+records=1 artifacts=3 committed=True pushed=True
+```
+
+Knowledge-bank commit:
+
+```text
+9e3a80d Add Pala Memory Core backup 2026-06-09-20260609T131949Z-pala-memory-core-backup
+```
+
+## Release Posture
+
+This is a preview connector. It intentionally avoids raw conversation backup and avoids pushing unless explicitly requested.
